crime_comedy.title: Crime Comedy
crime_comedy.description: Crime doesn’t pay, but it can make you laugh!

9352.title: Half a Sinner
9352.description: A young and beautiful school teacher Anne Gladden fears a dull future. She finally decides to take a walk on the wild side in order to find adventure, which is just what she finds.

299591.title: Suicide Kings
299591.description: A group of rich twenty-somethings kidnap a crime boss and use his money to pay a ransom for one of their sisters, who was also kidnapped.

300175.title: Stand Up Guys
300175.description: After one of them gets paroled, three retired gangsters reunite and reminisce as another ponders his next job — killing his old friend.

307755.title: Novocaine
307755.description: The hilarious Steve Martin stars in this darkly comic tale of a good man gone bad featuring Helena Bonham Carter, Laura Dern, and Scott Caan.

312179.title: Get Shorty
312179.description: A gangster goes to Hollywood to collect a debt and becomes a big-time producer when he realizes the movie business runs a lot like the mob.

314040.title: Violet & Daisy
314040.description: It was meant to be a straightforward job, but these teenage assassins are thrown for a loop when they target a mysterious loner in New York.

317189.title: Fatal Beauty
317189.description: When a tainted drug shipment hits the streets of L.A., a witty narcotics cop goes undercover to investigate in this fast-paced romantic comedy.

324856.title: Bank Roll
324856.description: Six friends have three days to pull off one heist.

341847.title: Lionhead
341847.description: Frank (Trevor Lissauer) desperately wants to marry his girlfriend, against the wishes of her father (Michael Madsen). When he buys a ring from a con artist (Brien Perry), criminal investigators (Daniel Roebuck, Deirdre Lovejoy), a lawyer (Richard Riehle), the mob and even the pizza boy get involved.

342093.title: Counterfeit Detective
342093.description: A security guard wanted to be a detective. He founded a detective agency when he was fired. However, he was involved in a kidnapping.

356526.title: Be Cool
356526.description: Chili Palmer turns to the world of rock stars, pop divas, and hip hop gangstas when a new idea for a movie leads him into the music business.

376106.title: I Went Down
376106.description: Irish action comedy written by Conor McPherson and directed by Paddy Breathnach, starring Brendan Gleeson and Peter McDonald. Git is an ex-con freshly released from a stint in prison. He soon finds himself thrust into the shady criminal underworld by crime boss Tom French, who forces him into taking on a task for him. He is teamed up with Bunny - a quick tempered brute who offed his own grandfather, and set the challenge of taking a hostage. Although their relationship gets off to a frosty start, the pair soon realise that if they are to survive the brutal underworld they must work together.

385363.title: Barney Thomson
385363.description: An awkward, diffident, Glasgow barber, lives a life of desperate mediocrity until he enters the grotesque and comically absurd world of the serial killer.

385502.title: Top Dog
385502.description: Maverick cop, Jake Wilder, is convinced his career is in jeopardy when he meets his new partner: a mischievous, high-I.Q. canine named Reno.

398666.title: BROADWAY'S FINEST
398666.description: Broadway's Finest is a diverting story about three struggling men who impersonate New York City under cover cops and chase down a notorious drug dealer in order to create their own cutting edge police drama. Desperate for success, they enter the dangerous world of undercover police work to get the authentic material they need to create their show. As the exploits of the ill-prepared detectives get them deeper and deeper into the case, they are driven to extremes. Do these guys really know what they're playing with? Will they survive the dangers of the street? Things are rarely what they seem in this gritty dramatic comedy.

402015.title: Too Fat Too Furious
402015.description: A clumsy, overweight criminal carrying a hefty debt teams up with a motley crew of undesirables to steal $300,000 to buy his father's new liver.

417608.title: Hoods
417608.description: A middle-aged mobster teams up with five would-be gangsters to take out the son of a rival mob boss, only to discover their target is a nine-year-old boy.

439637.title: Smartass
439637.description: A 15-year old runaway is released from jail after being arrested and hustled. Now she must navigate Murder City, 120 miles away from anyone familiar.

440279.title: London's Finest
440279.description: A dirty cop pursues a vendetta against some small time London drug-dealers hiding a shipment of heroin, along with the help of gun-toting roughnecks.

443633.title: Silver Bears
443633.description: When a shady but alluring duo, a prince and a wheeler-dealer, try to take over a Swiss bank, they end up with a silver mine and romantic problems.

449375.title: BLACKMALE
449375.description: Two desperate con men find themselves making a planned attempt to blackmail a dangerously psychotic doctor who just may be a serial killer.

452576.title: Flickering Lights
452576.description: They have always had each other, now they just have to find themselves.

456019.title: La Rancherita
456019.description: With her orphanage facing financial ruin, a desperate Tex-Mex singer embarks on a risky drug-running mission for a sinister rancher.

458488.title: Rim Shop
458488.description: Jo Jo has 24 hours to pay off a vicious loan shark, or lose his rim shop forever. His only hope is in the hands of his two idiotic friends.

460878.title: The Art of the Steal
460878.description: Loyalty and the bonds of brotherhood are tested when a high-stakes heist is planned by a crew of criminals, each with an ulterior motive.

461410.title: The Scenesters
461410.description: Crime-scene videographers try their hand at detective work, investigating the bizarre clues left by a serial killer butchering hipsters in East L.A.

462426.title: Assassination of a High School President
462426.description: At a Catholic high school, the popular girl teams up with a sophomore newspaper reporter to investigate a case of stolen SAT exams. Once the duo target their suspects, a larger conspiracy is unearthed.

463675.title: No Panic With a Hint of Hysteria
463675.description: A timid accountant tries to earn his living as a hitman, until he becomes a target for the vengeful mafia boss, murderous gangsters, mad cops and a sexy blonde - and if he's not careful his own wife might catch wind of his double life too.

466023.title: Running Scared
466023.description: Two policemen in wintry Chicago put off their tropical retirement plans when their nemesis, a ruthless drug dealer and murderer, evades custody.

466264.title: Miami Blues
466264.description: An unhinged ex-con takes a wild ride on both sides of the law, committing crimes, posing as a cop, and trying to romance the hooker he just met.

466329.title: 6 Dynamic Laws for Success (In Life, Love & Money)
466329.description: A lifelong loser discovers a coded message in a self-help book, revealing the location of millions in stolen cash. He's not the only one.

466552.title: Paint It Red
466552.description: When a struggling artist swipes some stolen loot, his apartment complex becomes a revolving crime scene as the thieves go hunting for the cash.

466930.title: The Great Texas Dynamite Chase
466930.description: After busting out of the big house, a sexy jailbird picks up a feisty hitchhiker for a bank robbing binge that will soon become legendary.

466932.title: The Fiction Makers
466932.description: Gentleman thief Simon Templar gets mistaken for a mystery novelist by a gang of crooks, who force him to plan an extravagant heist.

467014.title: Toy Gun
467014.description: The black-comic tale of a meek man, who robs a bank to prove his grit to his wife, finds him on terra nova with a bundle of cash and a new ex-con pal.

475482.title: Women Who Kill
475482.description: Locally famous true-crime podcasters, who are also ex-girlfriends, suspect a new love interest is a serial killer in this deadpan comedy.

476908.title: Killer Looks
476908.description: An alcoholic private detective and a sarcastic woman who loves kung-fu films team up to solve the murders of a fashion photographer and his models.

486598.title: Mad Dog Time
486598.description: After a mob boss is released from the mental hospital, his friends, family, and cronies, scramble to readjust the dynamics of their business.

489712.title: Random Acts of Violence
489712.description: A nostalgic New Yorker starts a violent crime wave that he hopes will drive down real estate prices and lure creative people back to the city.

489926.title: Avenging Angelo
489926.description: A dead mobster's daughter tries to reject her father's criminal past, but danger comes for her anyway, forcing a loyal bodyguard to intervene.

494830.title: Close But No Cigar
494830.description: A man and his dimwit companion help with the sale of an old VW van and are thrust into the clutches of criminals, debt collectors, and a psychopath.

495394.title: Bank Robber
495394.description: When a hopeless romantic tries to impress his thrill-seeking lover by robbing a bank, the heist goes wrong, sending him into hiding and another life.

495751.title: Freeway 2: Confessions of a Trickbaby
495751.description: A teen prostitute teams up with a serial killer to break out of prison and escape to Mexico. It’s an adventurous road movie like you've never seen.

496328.title: Dolemite
496328.description: Dolemite is the role that made Rudy Ray Moore a midnight-cult-film icon as a framed pimp who fights city corruption with his all-girl Kung-Fu killers.

499311.title: Down Terrace
499311.description: After a stint in prison, a small crime family struggles to stay in business while facing threats from an estranged girlfriend and an unknown mole.

499599.title: Why Siegfried Teitelbaum Had to Die
499599.description: After hitman Stefan survives an assassination attempt, he reports what he remembers to authorities, but his past is full of mystery and deception.

505248.title: Imperfections
505248.description: A struggling actress works with a diamond importer, but when she becomes involved in a heist, everything quickly spirals into chaos.

505253.title: Kid Cannabis
505253.description: For a high school dropout and his slacker friend, trafficking marijuana across the Canadian border seems like the perfect scheme...until it’s not.

505297.title: Stark Raving Mad
505297.description: A thief plans to rob the boss who murdered his brother, but first he has to assemble the ultimate heist team to execute his vision flawlessly.

510568.title: Daddy-O
510568.description: When a truck driver is offered a job singing in a nightclub, he quickly learns the new gig comes with some felonious strings attached.

511110.title: A Cool Fish
511110.description: A former cop turned security guard is sent back into police work after his sister is kidnapped. Can he save her before it’s too late?

512313.title: Soft Money
512313.description: A rich banker hires thieves to steal a million dollars from his own bank, but when he double-crosses the crooks, they hatch an elaborate revenge plot.

518720.title: The Act
518720.description: A caper full of wild intrigue includes a bribed US president, blackmail, prison escapes, and a complex heist, in a plot where nothing is as it seems.

519525.title: The Hot Potato
519525.description: In 1969 London, as the Beatles top the charts and the US and USSR vie for power, two East End lads try to find a buyer for a lump of stolen uranium.

522440.title: Vice Academy 5
522440.description: Sexy vice cops must stop a virtual reality prostitute’s crime spree when a police commissioner’s son somehow uploads her out of a naughty video game.

524398.title: Know Nothins
524398.description: Following a successful heist, five professionals celebrate in a summer home while they wait for the final piece of the plan to fall into place.

526257.title: Hot Guys With Guns
526257.description: The detective bug bites two ex-boyfriends who team up with a jaded private investigator to solve a robbery spree targeting a gay Hollywood sex club.

533445.title: So Undercover
533445.description: A young private eye is tasked with an undercover assignment at a college sorority house in order to protect the family member of a crucial witness.

533846.title: Jackpot
533846.description: When a man wakes up in a strip club surrounded by corpses, a wild battle of greed and betrayal involving a large sum of money ensues.

535964.title: Kill Your Friends
535964.description: A ruthless music exec searches for the last hit music act of the London pop scene while killing off any rivals in his drunken, drugged-out haze.

536585.title: Lucky Losers: Leo Gorcey & the Bowery Boys
536585.description: Slip and Sach suspect an illegal casino in the death of their boss so they go undercover as croupiers and a rich gambler to catch their criminals.

540196.title: Cain and Abel
540196.description: This modern LA tale with a strong '70's vibe, tells of an outlaw cop team on the hunt for a dangerous gangster with a gold-plated wheelchair.

543930.title: The Magician
543930.description: A charismatic, rough hitman in Melbourne, Australia hires his film student next-door neighbor to film a documentary about his darkly humorous life.

547021.title: El Investigador Capulina
547021.description: Creyendo que se las sabe de todas todas, se mete de detective, pero sus amigos los justicieros tendrán que salvarle el pellejo cada vez.

547042.title: Viruta Y Capulina: Dos Locos en Escena
547042.description: Dónde quedó el muertito, es lo que se pregunta el actor que puso en una caja a su compañero que se desplomó durante el ensayo de una obra de teatro.

556406.title: A Series of Bad Decisions
556406.description: The plan of an ambitious and sharp reporter to find a crime kingpin’s identity is turned on its head when her sponsor dies and she’s stuck in jail.

560096.title: Watch Out for the Automobile
560096.description: Yury, a 20th century Russian Robin Hood, is an insurance agent living a double life as a car thief who steals from rich crooks to help the poor.

560755.title: Badges of Fury (Dubbed)
560755.description: When a string of eerie murders haunts Hong Kong, two trouble-making cops discover that the victims were all ex-boyfriends of an aspiring starlet.

561230.title: Kill the Habit
561230.description: When a woman accidentally kills her drug dealer, she and her pals try to dispose of the corpse, as addicts looking for a fix keep getting in the way.

565625.title: The Diggers
565625.description: After a heist gone wrong, a criminal is forced to kill his partner and best friend. But when he delays, a cadre of colorful characters descend.

569474.title: Compadres
569474.description: Fast-paced comedy about a Mexican, no-nonsense police officer and an American teen computer hacker who team up for a crime boss’s downfall.

573797.title: Dead or Alive 2: Tôbôsha
573797.description: Two fearsome Yakuza assassin rivals decide to reunite as the childhood friends they are and start over in their homeland after a hit goes wrong.

574630.title: Black Out
574630.description: Retired criminal Jos wakes up the morning before his wedding to learn he has 24 hours to get a drug lord 20 kilos of cocaine or his bride-to-be dies.

576124.title: Loki 7
576124.description: Siete amigos acaban metidos en medio de un lío de mucho dinero entre un gángster ruso y otro dominicano que controlan el inframundo de Punta Cana.

577927.title: Bank Shot
577927.description: Fresh from his recent jailbreak, criminal mastermind Walter Ballantine (George C. Scott) is already plotting his next bank heist. And this time he's thinking big...he's not just taking the loot, he's stealing the whole bank! Beset by a hapless crew, a lusty backer and an overzealous prison warden, Ballantine soon discovers that when your getaway vehicle is the bank itself, it pays to be America's most driven criminal. Brimming with wonderful and imaginative silliness.

579564.title: N.Y.P.D. Mounted
579564.description: The unlikely partnership of a rodeo cowboy and a jaded cop lead to all sorts of hijinks in New York City’s horse-riding law enforcement unit.

581174.title: The Girl Gets Moe
581174.description: When a ruthless mobster falls in love, he tries to change his life. But when his partner makes a deadly mistake, his new love turns on him.

586158.title: Cop and a Half: New Recruit
586158.description: A jaded detective is partnered up with a 12-year-old, who proves her worth when it comes to investigating crimes and understanding technology.

586168.title: Cop and a Half
586168.description: After an observational eight-year-old witnesses a murder, a hard-boiled detective must take the child under his wing to solve the crime.

589103.title: Inner City Rats
589103.description: A comical and gritty slice-of-life look at life on the streets and behind closed doors in New York City, where gunplay, scams, and partying intersect.

589226.title: When Geek Meets Serial Killer
589226.description: A cartoonist accidentally kills his best friend, then learns that his friend slept with his girlfriend, attracting the attention of a serial killer.

590502.title: Rook.
590502.description: After a pair of siblings and a small group attempt a gold heist and miserably fail, they most contend with hillbilly brothers ready to fight back.

591183.title: The Black Ball
591183.description: A middle-aged shopkeeper goes way off the deep end to figure out why he got downvoted by a local members-only club he tried to join.

591820.title: First Love (Dubbed)
591820.description: Over the course of a single night in Tokyo, a young boxer and a sex worker meet in a whilrwind of romance and accidental drug smuggling.

593656.title: Snowman's Land
593656.description: After a professional killer botches a job, he heads to a remote region with his sidekick, but they soon realize that their bad luck doesn’t end there.

593857.title: Scotland, PA
593857.description: The classic intrigue of Shakespeare’s “Macbeth” comes to the suburbs of Philly in the 1970s as a hamburger vendor is influenced by his scheming wife.

596148.title: Terminal Exposure
596148.description: Two beach combing-shutterbugs accidentally capture a murder on film. Now detectives, the boys set out to capture a murderess shot only from behind, with a rose tattoo on her behind. Fun in the sun turns dangerous when they end up shooting bullets instead of film.

596982.title: Away Bus
596982.description: Two sisters need to raise money to save their dying mother. All attempts to help fail, so they decide to do the unthinkable, a highway bus robbery.

599232.title: Jerry Powell & the Delusions of Grandeur
599232.description: Jerry Powell is a gas-huffing thief with memory distrust syndrome. At the brink of insanity, Powell finds himself chased by a pulpy gang of criminals as he attempts to deliver a mysterious package for a money-launder.

601997.title: Night Shift
601997.description: When their mother dies, two destitute brothers rob a gas station to save their family home, but when things go wrong, they start taking hostages.

602993.title: Three Rookies
602993.description: A trio of losers with no money or job prospects become unlikely heroes after taking advantage of a staff shortage at the Atlanta Police Department.

604717.title: Clover
604717.description: Two brothers "Irish Twins"- down on their luck, and in debt to a dangerous crime boss, must go on the run to save themselves, and a seemingly innocent teenage girl, after a job goes wrong, and she kills the crime boss’s only son.

605637.title: A Nightingale Sang in Berkeley Square
605637.description: An American ex-con’s release from jail in England leads him to go straight but soon a local kingpin decides they should pull off a big bank heist.

605825.title: Parting Shots
605825.description: This star-studded ensemble comedy tells of a dying photographer and his elaborate plan to seek revenge against all who have wronged him.

606362.title: Have a Nice Day (Subbed)
606362.description: A gritty animated crime drama about a man who steals a million in cash from his boss and soon has equally greedy characters wanting it for themselves.

606427.title: Fishy Stones
606427.description: On the run after a jewelry store heist, two amateur thieves head to the countryside and dump their loot in some brush before being caught by police.

609482.title: Big City Blues
609482.description: A night in the big city becomes a rollercoaster of missed connections as two hitmen, a prostitute, and an LGBT couple head toward a final showdown.

610723.title: Silver Case
610723.description: A powerful and vengeful Hollywood producer plots to ruin an actor’s career by sending him a silver briefcase, setting off a chain of wacky events.

611691.title: Bulldog Drummond's Bride
611691.description: Crime fighter and contented bachelor Bulldog Drummond once again is prevented from marrying his girlfriend when a bank robbery in London pops off.

614146.title: I Am a Pig: Dirty Cop No Donut (Vol. 2)
614146.description: A greasy cop, out of jail after bullying perpetrators on video, gets back to his crimes as his cousin goes off and abducts a politician’s daughter.

614782.title: Mama Weed
614782.description: A translator with the Paris police (Isabelle Huppert) finds herself in possession of a huge store ofhash, the insider knowledge required to move it and an unexpected flair for the danger that ensues.

617337.title: Billion
617337.description: When a high-powered banker loses all of his wealth, he’ll need to call on his estranged children to help him carry out a heist of his own bank.

617518.title: Midnight Runners
617518.description: A pair of goofy students at a police academy witness a kidnapping and decide to solve the crime themselves, despite their lack of experience.

619484.title: Danny. Legend. God.
619484.description: A cocky businessman in Bulgaria takes a British journalist on the ride of a lifetime when he takes control of the writer’s documentary about him.

620085.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
620085.description: Action icon Donnie Yen stars as a super cop who becomes depressed and obese after a break-up and just before he gets a murder case to save his job.

622622.title: Amateur Crook
622622.description: The daughter of a miner who foolishly loaned a priceless diamond to two loan sharks is mistaken as a thief as well by a confused artist.

627965.title: Three Thieves
627965.description: A trio of frustrated friends is contacted for a simple robbery job. Although it’s a case of mistaken identity, they decide to take on the job anyway.

628039.title: Good Boys for Life
628039.description: A hustler runs into his ex-girlfriend’s baby daddy. Afraid for his life, he leaves town and is offered half a million bucks to kill a woman’s husband.

629134.title: Dymez
629134.description: Three desperate young women plan heists using an app on their smartphones, unaware of just how dangerous the situation is about to get.

630645.title: Super Hustle
630645.description: When a bush-league private eye teams up with a hapless street hustler, he must simultaneously navigate an impossible heist and his biggest-ever case.

632800.title: International Crime
632800.description: When an exploding safe kills a prominent banker, amateur detective Lamont Cranston’s investigation leads to a dangerous ring of international spies.

633063.title: A Wiseguy Christmas
633063.description: After a New York mob boss is put in the witness protection program and relocated to Los Angeles, he must reconsider his take on Christmas.

634422.title: A Stolen Jackpot
634422.description: Good guy Tom gets a hard lesson in luck and loss after a $350 million winning lottery ticket puts a target on his back by a motley crew of characters.

637069.title: 9 Stacks
637069.description: A young man finds himself caught up in a matter of business fraud and has to choose whether to call it out or try to escape the consequences.

639174.title: Where Sleeping Dogs Lie
639174.description: To pay off a crippling debt, Jeff’s girlfriend suggests stealing it from her wealthy developer husband in what becomes anything but an easy score.

641701.title: The Pharmacist
641701.description: A narcoleptic pharmacist with a drug-peddling side hustle tries to ditch dealing for his new girlfriend, but a psychotic killer has other plans.

641836.title: Handlebar
641836.description: Two bumbling thieves are hired by an inner city crime boss to kidnap a rival's daughter. They end up inadvertently kidnapping his daughter.

642395.title: Good Thief
642395.description: After three small-time criminals knock off a pawnbroker for a valuable baseball card collection, they realize they’re in deeper than they thought.

646863.title: BMX Bandits
646863.description: A trio of teen BMX enthusiasts finds themselves in the crossfires of a group of bank robbers after they sell their stash of walkie-talkies.

647716.title: The Benefit List
647716.description: A top-tier life insurance agent goes on a search for a killer when the uber famous artists on her client list start getting picked off, one by one.

647881.title: Toro Loco: Bloodthirsty
647881.description: A stranger comes to a crime-ridden town and enlists the help of a young woman and a trigger-happy drag queen to avenge the murder of his son.

648147.title: Trick or Treat
648147.description: The life of a sleep-deprived new dad is turned upside down when his brother shows up on Halloween with the body of a gangster’s son in his trunk.

655403.title: SGT. Kabukiman N.Y.P.D.
655403.description: An ancient prophecy transforms a bumbling NYPD detective into the world's oddest superhero to take on evil corporations and drug-dealing ministers.

662529.title: Tinseltown
662529.description: Suspecting that their neighbor is an infamous serial killer, two down-and-out Hollywood screenwriters use his exploits as inspiration for a script.

664037.title: Dirty Cop No Donut
664037.description: A demented police officer goes over the edge and exacts his brand of violent and brutal justice on society while engaging in sex and drugs.

664168.title: American Dream
664168.description: When a small-time drug dealer steals a shipment, he and his roommate unwittingly leave a trail of clues that lead the gang’s henchmen to their door.

667942.title: Honest
667942.description: In late-1960’s swinging London, the All Saints girls play three streetwise sisters who head 'up West' to cheat, steal and generally cause trouble.

667956.title: The Young Poisoner's Handbook
667956.description: Inspired by the true story of a British teen with a morbid curiosity about chemically induced murder who allegedly poisoned those closest to him.

672671.title: Good Girls Don't
672671.description: A bold and daring stripper and mousey secretary go on the lam in a red convertible after being framed for a murder they didn't commit.

675221.title: Subway
675221.description: On improvising a burglary at a shady tycoon's home, Fred takes refuge in the hip and surreal universe of the Paris Metro and meets unique individuals.

676862.title: 68 Kill
676862.description: A robbery gone wrong sends a hapless guy and his psychotic girlfriend on a seriously wild ride in this deranged, off-the-rails blast of insanity.

677077.title: Arizona
677077.description: In this darkly comedic story, Cassie, a real estate agent and single mom, struggles to keep it all together during the housing crisis of 2009.

678308.title: Moonlighting Mistress
678308.description: When two burglars throw a wrench in Jan's plan to get rid of his controlling wife, he enlists his mistress to impersonate her and grab the money.

679422.title: The Mandarin Mystery
679422.description: Detective Ellery Queen investigates two murders and the theft of a missing, rare Chinese stamp valued at $50,000 in the penthouse of a hotel.

680568.title: Super
680568.description: A super-entertaining action fantasy about a down-on-his-luck fry cook who becomes a homegrown masked avenger and puts an end to crimes.

680756.title: Absolute Debauchery
680756.description: After losing $60k of their ruthless boss's money on a card game, two crooks go on the run through L.A.'s dangerous and bizarre criminal underworld.

681442.title: Pep Squad
681442.description: Despite not being nominated, a young woman vying for the title of prom queen resorts to murder and mayhem to get it in this over-the-top B-movie.

682042.title: Once Upon a Time in Venice
682042.description: Venice Beach P.I. Steve Ford is a detective who's good with the ladies, bad with the punches, and absolutely wild about his dog, Buddy.

685148.title: Trapped by Television
685148.description: An inventor looking for backing for his television invention gets involved with a crooked businessman and gangsters who try to steal his invention.

685537.title: Taskforce Neighbors
685537.description: After getting a bit off rails from eating contaminated raisins, three suburban dads team up to fight the local Russian mob boss in this comedy.

688876.title: Up in the Air
688876.description: When a none-too-popular singer is murdered on the air in a radio studio, a page boy and his janitor pal work together to find the killer.

692257.title: Gangster Exchange
692257.description: A Tokyo punk-Yakuza and a Bosnian mob enforcer are on the run when a deal goes sideways to smuggle a million-dollar toilet made of heroin to New York.

693629.title: Last Day of Summer
693629.description: This story follows an agitated fast-food employee, Joe, who decides to take revenge on his boss after reaching his breaking point.

693890.title: Tomorrow's Today
693890.description: Two lovable grifters rob a liquor store to pay a gambling debt to a savage crime boss only to learn the liquor store they rob is owned by the mobster.

695065.title: Killer Whales
695065.description: A naive and painfully unprepared filmmaker sets out to make the next true crime blockbuster and nearly ends up incarcerated in the process.

695463.title: Culture Shock
695463.description: A London trip for four college grads turns into the chase of a lifetime as they get caught up in a series of murders and an international crime ring.

695949.title: Low Heat
695949.description: Quick-witted Jamal runs afoul of the city’s dangerous crime boss after getting mixed up with a pair of careless dealers in a drug deal-gone-bad.

696346.title: The Stoolie
696346.description: A New Jersey police informant steals money from a sting operation and runs off to Florida with the case detective on his tail.

696722.title: Dinero Fácil (Doblado)
696722.description: Tras la muerte de su padre, un grupo de hermanos trabaja para un servicio de limpieza de oficinas donde uno de ellos decide ganar dinero fácil.

697775.title: Loose Change
697775.description: A down-on-his-luck street magician and his con artist ex-wife reunite to swindle an accounting firm in this dark comedy.

701355.title: Izzy & Moe
701355.description: The adventures of a pair of retired vaudeville performers who become two of the best prohibition agents during New York City’s roaring 1920s.

701693.title: Crime Spree
701693.description: A bumbling gang of French thieves travels to Chicago for a one-time foolproof job only to find themselves pawns in a set-up involving a mafioso.

702506.title: Murder of a Cat
702506.description: In his quest to find out who shot an arrow through his beloved pet cat, a distraught slacker and his unexpected ally stumble across a conspiracy.

702978.title: Going by the Book
702978.description: Things get out of control when a saintly traffic cop is asked to play the role of the bank robber in a theft intervention police training program.

703203.title: Troll-a-Long With a Rent-a-Cop: A Thug Life Tour Guide to the Reno City Zoo
703203.description: Agent Beacon went undercover to investigate organized crime in a small Nevada town, where he discovered a multi-state drug trafficking operation.

703744.title: Mission Possible
703744.description: A private investigator and a secret agent join forces to investigate an arms trafficking case while trying to avoid putting themselves in harm's way.

705185.title: The Golden Boys
705185.description: Out for the reward and the glory, lifelong friends Hans and Antho set out to catch a serial bank robber under the watchful eye of law enforcement.

707371.title: Habit
707371.description: A drug deal gone wrong sends a streetwise party girl and her friends on the run and into hiding at a convent from a vengeful Los Angeles drug lord.

708805.title: Susie Q
708805.description: Two down-and-out brothers spend their days fighting over the attentions of a neighborhood girl while plotting how to rob her.

710276.title: Godspeed
710276.description: A novice drug mule and hapless cabbie pair up through accidental circumstances to help each other survive a shockingly violent delivery gone wrong.

711330.title: Bring Me the Head of the Machine Gun Woman
711330.description: Looking to regain power, the mob puts out a notice to every hitman in the city: $1 million for the sexy mercenary killing any criminal with a bounty.

711837.title: Lava
711837.description: A trippy and bleakly comic crime thriller follows lives recklessly fated when a botched vendetta spirals absurdly and violently out of control.

716292.title: Burglar
716292.description: Just when a San Francisco bookstore owner is set to give up her side hustle as a burglar, a crooked cop blackmails her into committing one more heist.

724579.title: Golden Years

100000579.title: Argo 2 (Español)
100000579.description: Después de estropear un robo, Tibi se convierte en el objetivo de asesinos japoneses, una familia gitana furiosa y el ejército eslovaco.

100001165.title: You Kill Me
100001165.description: A killer comedy about a hitman whose drinking is getting in the way of his killing: it will take AA and the love of a woman to get him back on track.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001652.title: Quik Money
100001652.description: After a close brush with the law, a hustler reinvents himself as a tax guru and finds himself reaping big rewards and taking on bigger risks.

100001934.title: Killin Smallz
100001934.description: With cash flow running dry, a struggling mob family hatches a scheme to kidnap a celebrity and hold them for ransom.

100003009.title: Like a Dirty French Novel

100003115.title: Gimme the Loot
100003115.description: Two fledgling graffiti artists make a high-stakes gamble that a risky scheme will turn them into the most famous street artists in New York City.

0300005273.title: Bounty Hunters

0300007975.title: America's Dumbest Criminals

0300008794.title: Filth City

0300009218.title: Swedish Dicks

0300007390.title: 24 Hour Rental

0300004988.title: Fugget About It

0300007425.title: Mr. and Mrs. North
